thread.title_full: American Frame americanframe.com reviewed by Mary

author: Mary
title: Mary
text: We priced frames at Michael's & a local frame shop but then I remembered years ago I had ordered from American frame & am so happy I did. The wood frame made to size is great quality & the price is a fraction of the estimates we had been given. Plus it was shipped quickly.
